nd Gestaltungsvorschläge entwickelt werden. So wird durchgehend ein enger Zusammenhang zwischen typischen Praxisfragen und gründlichen rechtlichen Ausführungen dazu gewährleistet.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aErbrecht. 4aPraxishandbuch. 4aTestament. 4aUnternehmensnachfolge. 4aVermögensübertragung. 4aletztwillige Verfügung. 7aLAW / Civil Law.2bisacsh1 aBeil, Herbert, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEdenfeld, Stefan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEndemann, Thomas, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEsser, Antje, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aFröhler, Oliver, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGrieger, Wolfgang, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGroll, Klaus Michael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGrötsch, Paul, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHieke, Manfred, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHoffmann, Beate, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHolzer, Anna, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKindler, Peter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKrauß, Hans-Frieder, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKränzle, Michael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMalzahn, Michael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMorgen, Robert D., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMuscheler, Karlheinz, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aNienaber, Susanne, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRuby, Gerhard, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.g